      <title>Xcode和Jenkins持续集成的几种实现方式</title>
      <link>https://huos3203.github.io/post/macos/xcode%E5%92%8Cjenkins%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E9%9B%86%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E5%87%A0%E7%A7%8D%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F/</link>
